cpl.readme: Provides the [[iPlayer-inspired Video.js skin|https://github.com/VD39/videojs-iplayer-skin-1]] (~GitHub) by [[Vijay Dubb/VD39|https://github.com/VD39]] (~GitHub) for use with the [[TwTube plugin|https://github.com/TheDiveO/TwTube]] (//you guessed right// ... ~GitHub). Simply install this plugin into your ~TiddlyWiki alongside the ~TwTube plugin and you're done.
